These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, tiparillo, oliveros
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
3 different games are played: canasta, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the fan of trance is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | baccarat   | oliveros   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Game     | snooker     | canasta      | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
3 different games are played: whist, chess, billiard
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, scientific
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the person watching epic movies is between the person playing chess and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Game   | chess     | billiard     | whist      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Movie-Genre           | scientific | epic     | disaster       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, coffee
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, january
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the bartender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the paramedic and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage          | cola  | coffee     | fanta     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Birthday   | september  | may    | january |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, tram
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, march, june
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person driving the tram is between the paramedic and the person who's birthday is in august##2
4. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport    | snowmobile       | tram  | van   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Birthday     | march   | june | august        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

