.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, photography
City: paris, london, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, poppy
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person who growsrose is between the person traveling to colone and the person who's hobby is photography##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growstulip##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Hobby         | cooking | filmmaking | photography |
| City   | colone  | london       | paris       |
| Flower           | tulip     | rose       | poppy     |

