There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, grey
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, daisy
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the fan of country is between the person eating pineapple and the person who growsiris##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Color         | pink | grey      | light-blue |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Flower           | orchid      | daisy       | iris      |

