The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person who likes apricot is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Color      | grey    | apricot          | blue |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Transport           | tram | helicopter | subway         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

