.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
City: marseilles, paris, prague
House: wooden, futuristic, ranch-style
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is the ranch-style house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the wooden house is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person traveling to marseilles##2
4. the futuristic house is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person drinking milk and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| City         | paris   | prague | marseilles |
| House   | futuristic        | wooden       | ranch-style      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

