.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, blues
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, pall-mall
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the fan of soul is the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the fan of dubstep is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the pall-mall-smoker and the fan of soul##2
6. the fan of blues is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Music-Genre       | soul | blues   | dubstep   |
| Cigar   | oliveros          | alhambra     | pall-mall       |

 